  "text": "To the best of the authors' knowledge, the only study dedicated to the question of existence and uniqueness of solutions to the non-local Eringen's model given by equation (2) is by Altan [CITATION_1] . This study focuses on the case of homogeneous Dirichlet boundary conditions, that is, G D = G and u = 0. We will now briefly recall the approach taken by Altan [CITATION_2] .",
